WEBVTT

00:10:29.400 --> 00:10:30.800
The last country --

00:10:32.000 --> 00:10:37.016
the last country in the world
who abolished slavery

00:10:37.040 --> 00:10:39.360
is the country where I was born,

00:10:39.920 --> 00:10:41.120
Brazil.

00:10:42.440 --> 00:10:47.200
We still have to work hard
to abolish discrimination.

00:10:48.080 --> 00:10:52.056
That remains a common practice worldwide,

00:10:52.080 --> 00:10:55.680
and that will not disappear by itself.

00:10:56.480 --> 00:10:57.736
Thank you.

00:10:57.760 --> 00:11:11.830
(Applause)